                              $this->indent - Topiramate: Topamax<BR>
                              $this->indent - Valproic Acid: Depakote<BR>
                              $this->indent - Zonisamide: Zonegran</h5>");

        $group[] =& $this->form->createElement(
            "static",
            null,
            null,
            "Medication");
        $group[] =& $this->form->createElement(
            "static",
            null,
            null,
